data.description: RARE FIND - Large home in desirable Ravenwood! Come see this spacious home with 2 living areas, 2 dining areas, full finished basement and the perfect set up with the master on the first floor and 4 more bedrooms upstairs! Soaring beamed ceilings and a grand wood burning fireplace in the living room greet you as you enter. The kitchen and living room open out to the deck and back yard. Great for barbecuing and entertaining! The kitchen has lots of storage, wall oven, built in microwave, and glass cooktop. All stainless appliances stay. The formal dining room off the entry could also make a great home office. The master with new vinyl plank flooring has a walk-in closet, large soaking tub with skylight and a walk-in shower. Upstairs there is a full renovated bath, 3 bedrooms and one extra large room without a closet which could be made into a bedroom or TV room. The finished basement is large with its own gas fireplace, wet bar and full bathroom. It was a game room but could be made into in-law quarters. There is also a shop in the basement. The yard has a deck and small gazebo, mature trees for shade, grass for kids and pets to run around, and is fully fenced for backyard fun. There are beds for gardening at the back fence and there is also room for boat parking behind the fence at the side yard. This home has so much to offer!!! Fresh exterior and interior paint in most rooms.
